Class ControlPanel

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ControlPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Creates the control panel, which contains buttons like "play", "pause" and "step", which can start, pause or step the Simulator.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
